about.summary: Simple interface routines to facilitate the handling of network objects with complex intertemporal data. This is a part of the "statnet" suite of packages for network analysis.

name: r-networkdynamic
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.10.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-networkdynamic
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/networkDynamic_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/networkDynamic/networkDynamic_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 22eed8d9dea8d70877c1619eb2bc3f1ac5142ce3db6fd6eb3e0879ca56b76ca0

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-network >=1.15
    - r-statnet.common
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-network >=1.15
    - r-statnet.common

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('networkDynamic')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('networkDynamic')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://statnet.org
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Simple interface routines to facilitate the handling of network objects with complex
    intertemporal data. This is a part of the "statnet" suite of packages for network
    analysis.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
